=== Reduce, reuse, repair and recycle ===

Recycling has been compulsory in the borough of Brent since 2008.Through a green box collection scheme the borough aims to improve on the 25 per cent recycled waste it already achieves. <ref>[[wikipedia:London Borough of Brent#Compulsory recycling]]</ref>

=== Social inclusion ===

Brent is the joint fourth-worst Borough in London for levels of child poverty. Save the Children reported in 2011 that 11,000 children are impoverished. <ref>[[wikipedia:London Borough of Brent#Economy]]</ref>

